videos.headline: Glass keeps it himself for Eastern Michigan TD
videos.description: Eastern Michigan's Mike Glass III follows his blockers on a QB keeper and powers into the end zone for the first touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Glass keeps it himself for Eastern Michigan TD) 2019/12/26

videos.headline: Pitt airs it out for 96-yard TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Kenny Pickett goes deep to connect with Maurice Ffrench, who outruns the defense for the 96-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt airs it out for 96-yard TD) 2019/12/26

videos.headline: Williams reels in tipped pass for Eastern Michigan score
videos.description: Mike Glass III has his pass tipped by a defender, but Quian Williams hauls in the pass anyway and takes it to the house for a 50-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams reels in tipped pass for Eastern Michigan score) 2019/12/26

videos.headline: Glass hits Jackson for Eastern Michigan TD
videos.description: Mike Glass III throws over the middle to connect with Arthur Jackson III for a 10-yard score, giving the Eagles a 27-20 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Glass hits Jackson for Eastern Michigan TD) 2019/12/26

videos.headline: Pitt ties game as Wayne dives into end zone
videos.description: Kenny Pickett throws a dart to Jared Wayne, who gets past two defenders and stretches into the end zone for the game-tying 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt ties game as Wayne dives into end zone) 2019/12/26

videos.headline: Ffrench passes Fitzgerald for Pitt's reception record
videos.description: Maurice Ffrench hauls in his 93rd reception of the season, passing Larry Fitzgerald for the most receptions in a single season in Pittsburgh history.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ffrench passes Fitzgerald for Pitt's reception record) 2019/12/26

videos.headline: Pitt takes late lead on Mack's incredible end zone grab
videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Kenny Pickett throws to the end zone for Taysir Mack, who makes an acrobatic catch for the go-ahead touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt takes late lead on Mack's incredible end zone grab) 2019/12/26

videos.headline: EMU QB ejected after punches thrown, ref hit in face
videos.description: Eastern Michigan QB Mike Glass III loses his temper late, throwing multiple punches and accidentally hitting a referee in the face.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (EMU QB ejected after punches thrown, ref hit in face) 2019/12/26
